    "title": "Zawadi ya Unabii",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "zawadi ya unabii",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kama mtume Petro alivyosema siku ya Pentekoste, unabii ulikuwa ni matokeo ya Roho Mtakatifu wa Mungu kumwagwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:21\">Matendo 2:17–21</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">Yoeli 2:28–32</a>). Kitabu cha Matendo kinataja manabii wachache Wakristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:28\">Matendo 11:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1\">13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:9-Acts21:11\">21:9–11</a>; tazama pia <em>The Martyrdom of Polycarp</em> 12:3; 16:2). Mmoja wa manabii hawa alikuwa Agabo, ambaye alitenda kama nabii wa Agano la Kale kwa kufanya matendo ya mfano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:10-Acts21:11\">Matendo 21:10–11</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:29-1Kgs11:32\">1 Wafalme 11:29–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:2-Isa20:6\">Isaiah 20:2–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:1-Jer13:11\">Yeremia 13:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:1-Ezek5:17\">Ezekieli 4:1–5:17</a>). Pia alitabiri matukio ya baadaye (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">Matendo 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:10-Acts21:11\">21:10–11</a>).</p><p>Filipo Mwinjilisti alikuwa na binti wanne &quot;walio na kipawa cha unabii&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:9\">Matendo 21:9</a>). Mtume Paulo pia alitambua kwamba baadhi ya wanawake Wakristo walikuwa na kipawa hiki cha unabii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:5\">1 Wakorintho 11:5</a>). Katika Agano la Kale, manabii wengi walikuwa wanaume, lakini baadhi ya wanawake pia walikuwa manabii, kama vile Miriamu, Debora, na Hulda (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">Kutoka 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:4\">Waamuzi 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:14-2Kgs22:20\">2 Wafalme 22:14–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:22-2Chr34:28\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 34:22–28</a>). Katika Agano Jipya, wanaume na wanawake, vijana na wazee, wanapokea kipawa cha unabii, kama Petro alivyotaja katika mahubiri yake siku ya Pentekoste (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:18\">Matendo 2:17–18</a>).</p><p>Unabii wakati mwingine unahusisha kutabiri siku zijazo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22-Acts20:23\">Matendo 20:22–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:10-Acts21:11\">21:10–1</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:24-Rom9:33\">Warumi 9:24–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:17\">1 Wathesalonike 4:13–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2 Wathesalonike 2:3–4</a>). Kimsingi, unabii unahusu kushiriki ujumbe wa Mungu kwa kuhubiri, kuhimiza, na kuelezea mapenzi ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">Matendo 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6\">Warumi 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:3-1Cor14:4\">1 Wakorintho 14:3–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:29-1Cor14:33\">29–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:10\">Ufunuo 19:10</a>). Kipawa cha unabii kinatajwa waziwazi katika barua za 1 Wakorintho na Waefeso kama moja ya vipawa vya Roho Mtakatifu na Yesu kwa kanisa lake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:11\">1 Wakorintho 12:4–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11\">Waefeso 4:11–13</a>). Kinalenga kufaidisha Wakristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:22\">1 Wakorintho 14:22</a>).</p><p>Unabii unapaswa kupimwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:19-1Thess5:21\">1 Wathesalonike 5:19–21</a>). Kanisa linapewa onyo kali kuhusu manabii wa uongo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1\">1 Yohana 4:1</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20-Rev2:23\">Ufunuo 2:20–23</a>). Wakristo wanapaswa kutumia kipawa hiki kwa uaminifu, kama Maandiko na Roho wa Mungu vinavyoelekeza. Kushiriki kwa ujasiri ukweli wa Mungu husaidia kanisa kuelewa mapenzi ya Mungu na kuwahamasisha watu kutii.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">Kutoka 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:5\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 13:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:4\">Waamuzi 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:29-1Kgs11:32\">1 Wafalme 11:29–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:14-2Kgs22:20\">2 Wafalme 22:14–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:2-Isa20:6\">Isaya 20:2–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:25\">44:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:1-Jer13:11\">Yeremia 13:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:25-Jer23:32\">23:25–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:1-Ezek4:17\">Ezekieli 4:1–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:2-Ezek13:9\">13:2–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">Yoeli 2:28–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">Mathayo 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">24:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:21\">Matendo 2:17–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:28\">11:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1\">13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:23\">20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:9-Acts21:11\">Matendo 21:9–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6\">Warumi 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:5\">1 Wakorintho 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:11\">12:4–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1-1Cor14:40\">14:1–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:13\">Waefeso 4:11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:19-1Thess5:21\">1 Wathesalonike 5:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2 Petro 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">1 Yohana 4:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20-Rev2:23\">Ufunuo 2:20–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:10\">19:10</a></p>",
